{"tid":1887892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湖北新增349, 湖北內既武漢新增615 ? 有冇數學家解釋下","createTime":"2020-02-20T00:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T05:09:02.000Z","uid":274996,"like":159,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"30e2abd8336bb23f251358e75b7fa698653773ef","tid":1887892,"uid":274996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T00:45:57.000Z","msg":"有冇數學家解釋下？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n湖北省衞健委公佈，武漢肺炎疫情全省周三再添349宗死亡個案，累計死亡人數達2,029人。然而，細看省內各市新增確診數字，竟發現武漢市有615宗，大大多於全省的數字。原來其中有玄機！由於內地再次調整統計標準，以致其他城市確診數字減少，官方就將各市確診個案「加減」後，得出349這個字。<br />\n<br />\n原本湖北省數字應將各市增加個案加起來計算，但今天官方公佈的數字更改統計標準，竟以各市的「相差數」來計算，將有新增個案的武漢市、隨州市、襄陽市、十堰市、仙桃市的數字總和，減去孝感市、黃岡市、荊州市、鄂州市等10個城市的「核減數」，結果就出現了全省確診數字細於武漢市的不正常情況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200220&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60618381\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200220%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60618381&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5EVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=66c31fa3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200220%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60618381&h=1728203a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200220&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60618381</a>"},{"pid":"6a6b9c9a3d8a19b42443e2474ac5e560e8a292b2","tid":1887892,"uid":297897,"like":112,"dislike":1,"score":111,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T00:47:29.000Z","msg":"武漢獨立"},{"pid":"d5846c313fb32a2311de83635482a0236483bb2a","tid":1887892,"uid":70301,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T00:48:07.000Z","msg":"因為武獨立咗，Republic of Wuhan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae1786fcbf8e0d90e5301fa3a949d72bec69431","tid":1887892,"uid":158,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T00: