n<br />\n深圳個確診同死亡無計入廣東省<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T01:06:59.000Z","msg":"深圳係直轄市"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T01:59:36.000Z","msg":"賊圳唔係直轄市，只係經濟特區，財政上稅不繳省"},{"pid":"b22706cb5d12b38b9d6d25971977e0020bddf0e6","tid":1887892,"uid":307898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T02:01:42.000Z","msg":"「資訊戰」有個痴線佬準備好曬中宣部旗下youtuber既report link<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1883056\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1883056</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"82b6686167220058ce0c994e2009a9c22f01a881","tid":1887892,"uid":86898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T02:01:43.000Z","msg":"睇文章，核減數=先加後減<br />\n即係一開始就將確診人數+懷疑人數加晒<br />\n然後當證明懷疑個案係無事，就減返<br />\n<br />\neg. <br />\nday 1<br />\n確診100人，懷疑100人<br />\n+200<br />\n累積 200人<br />\n<br />\nday 2<br />\n懷疑中既50人測試陰性<br />\n-50<br />\n累積 150人"},{"pid":"83b11e81155b23bd8f1afc482438ccb9a49514a7","tid":1887892,"uid":194130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8805920d7dd6c583a001b999765d80dbc533ce1","tid":1887892,"uid":41873,"like":4,"dislike":44,"score":-40,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T00:56:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再推肺炎post啦好嗎</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T02:04:57.000Z","msg":"好啦我唔推肺炎post<br />\n我推武漢化武post"},{"pid":"7ec9e4babe31fcb109fe226d8a818da4ecf80371","tid":1887892,"uid":274055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30e2abd8336bb23f251358e75b7fa698653773ef","tid":1887892,"uid":274996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T00:45:57.000Z","msg":"有冇數學家解釋下？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n湖北省衞健委公佈，武漢肺炎疫情全省周三再添349宗死亡個案，累計死亡人數達2,029人。然而，細看省內各市新增確診數字，竟發現武漢市有615宗，大大多於全省的數字。原來其中有玄機！由於內地再次調整統計標準，以致其他城市確診數字減少，官方就將各市確診個案「加減」後，得出349這個字。<br />\n<br />\n原本湖北省數字應將各市增加個案加起來計算，但今天官方公佈的數字更改統計標準，竟以各市的「相差數」來計算，將有新增個案的武漢市、隨州市、襄陽市、十堰市、仙桃市的數字總和，減去孝感市、黃岡市、荊州市、鄂州市等10個城市的「核減數」，結果就出現了全省確診數字細於武漢市的不正常情況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200220&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60618381\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200220%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60618381&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5EVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=66c31fa3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200220%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60618381&h=1728203a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200220&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60618381</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T02:05:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.nhc.gov.cn/xcs/yqtb/202002/4dcfcb9b74ea4a408fc1d56d4db61f93.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhc.gov.cn%2Fxcs%2Fyqtb%2F202002%2F4dcfcb9b74ea4a408fc1d56d4db61f93.shtml&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5EVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=469ae7c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.nhc.gov.cn/xcs/yqtb/202002/4dcfcb9b74ea4a408fc1d56d4db61f93.shtml</a><br />\n武汉新增615例，仙桃等4市新增13例，荆门、咸宁等10市州对确诊病例中来源于原&ldquo;临床诊断病例&rdquo;者进行核酸检测，通过综合分析，将核酸检测结果为阴性的病例从确诊病例中核减，共订正核减279例<br />\n<br />\n【肺炎預報】<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ofRpaFX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ofRpaFX</a>"},{"pid":"28900eed088dc26336a787c74ef35fdfe820ec78","tid":1887892,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T02:11:46.000Z","msg":"成件事好奇怪，當話要強制復工後，確診人數明顯減少。但有想斷網"},{"pid":"151d0af1ff29890acf85e01f2168644fcab8ed29","tid":1887892,"uid":60860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T02:19:30.000Z","msg":"可加可減機制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68cf8136315824970a1392093b3af3a484acfb80","tid":1887892,"uid":199540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"489e406a57e4ebd79166b5b8efab954b0c83bff7","tid":1887892,"uid":2267,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c45f3218d3b07899d85